The paper discusses challenges and pitfalls in reproducing machine learning artifacts, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as examples of areas where ML artifacts are being proposed. Additionally, the paper discusses the issue of non-reproducible procedures, which is a common problem in software engineering (cs.SE).
